result.name: Forbidden Duck

reviews.text: Very tasty and formal roasted duck! A very delight surprise! The roasted duck is one of the best u can find in town. Fairly priced considering it is located in Causeway Bay... Not cheap though... Will come again...
Will definitely be back. Best char siu!
Very nice food, especially the char siu. Wonderful 😋👍

This is a new horizon of tasting Peking Duck. Slow-cooked the Duck first and then roast it. Very good!!! 

Apart from Peking Duck, other dishes are also brilliant. You can’t miss the rice with seafood broth. It’s excellent!!!

Convenient location with fancy decorations. A bit overpriced for the food quality. From their name you would expect the duck dishes to be fantastic, sadly that’s not really the case. Through my years of observation restaurants with this level of food quality don’t tend to last in Times Square for long.

reviews.text: 鴨要訂又不在訂位時說😠賣曬
好食，但餐飯食左4-5位數（8個大人，4個細路

Very tasty and formal roasted duck! A very delight surprise! The roasted duck is one of the best u can find in town. Fairly priced considering it is located in Causeway Bay... Not cheap though... Will come again...
Will definitely be back. Best char siu!
片皮鴨，皮片得很薄，肥糕應該處理過，所以食落冇吟油膩，如果可以再熱小小會更好，鸭湯泡飯很好吃，炸過旣米飯加飯混在一起，口感好特別！贊
